<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your stylesheet -->
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>
            <h4 style="color: dodgerblue">INFINITE COMPUTER SOLUTIONS</h4>

            <p>

                Infinite Computer Solution is your trusted partner in navigating the digital landscape. We specialize in innovative IT solutions that drive business success and efficiency.
            </p>

            <p>
                <strong>What We Do:</strong><br>

                IT Consulting: Tailored strategies to enhance your technology.<br>

                Software Development: Custom applications designed for your needs.<br>

                Managed Services: Reliable support to keep your IT running smoothly.<br>

                Cybersecurity: Advanced protection to safeguard your business.<br>

                Cloud Solutions: Scalable and flexible cloud services.
            </p>

            <p>

                Our Mission is to empower businesses with cutting-edge technology and exceptional service. At Infinite Computer Solution, we blend expertise with innovation to deliver solutions that exceed expectations.
            </p>

            <p>
                <strong>Why Choose Us?</strong> We’re committed to your success with a focus on integrity, excellence, and customer satisfaction. Let’s transform your tech challenges into opportunities for growth.
            </p>

            <p>

                Contact Us today to discover how we can help you thrive in the digital age.
            </p>

            <!-- New section for Addresses -->
            <h3 class="section-title">Our Locations</h3>
            <div class="address-cards">
                <div class="address-card">
                    <h4 class="address-title">Chennai Office</h4>
                    <p><strong>Street:</strong> MEPZ</p>
                    <p><strong>City:</strong> Chennai</p>
                    <p><strong>State:</strong> Tamilnadu</p>
                    <p><strong>ZipCode:</strong> 98052-6399</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> 425.555.0101</p>
                </div>
                <div class="address-card">
                    <h4 class="address-title">Hyderabad Office</h4>
                    <p><strong>Street:</strong> Perkit Road</p>
                    <p><strong>City:</strong> Hyderabad</p>
                    <p><strong>State:</strong> Telangana</p>
                    <p><strong>ZipCode:</strong> 503224</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> 425.555.0102</p>
                </div>
                <div class="address-card">
                    <h4 class="address-title">Bangalore Office</h4>
                    <p><strong>Street:</strong> EPIP Zone Whitefield Rd</p>
                    <p><strong>City:</strong> Bangalore</p>
                    <p><strong>State:</strong> Karnataka</p>
                    <p><strong>ZipCode:</strong> 98054-6399</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> 425.555.0103</p>
                </div>
                <div class="address-card">
                    <h4 class="address-title">Noida Office</h4>
                    <p><strong>Street:</strong> Noida Main A-block</p>
                    <p><strong>City:</strong> Noida</p>
                    <p><strong>State:</strong> UttarPradesh</p>
                    <p><strong>ZipCode:</strong> 98054-7899</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> 425.666.9999</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
<style>
    /* General Container Styles */
    body {
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        background-image: url('https://www.the-corporate.com/public/profile_images/41765-1711004313.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        background-position: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

.container {

    width: 80%;

    margin: auto;

    padding: 20px;

    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #e2e3e5); /* Light gradient background */

}

/* About Section Styles */

.about-section {

    background-color: #ffffff; /* White background for readability */

    padding: 20px;

    border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */

    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Enhanced shadow */

}

/* Section Title Styles */

.section-title {

    margin-top: 30px;

    font-size: 1.5rem;

    color: #28a745; /* Vibrant Green */

    border-bottom: 3px solid #28a745; /* Green underline */

    padding-bottom: 10px;

    font-weight: bold;

    text-transform: uppercase;

}

/* About Heading Styles */

.about-section h2 {

    color: green; /* Bright Blue for main heading */

    font-size: 2.5rem;

    border-bottom: 3px solid red; /* Blue underline */

    padding-bottom: 10px;

    margin-bottom: 20px;

}

.about-section h4 {

    color: #ff6f61; /* Coral for sub-heading */

    font-size: 1.8rem;

    margin-bottom: 15px;

}

/* Paragraph Styles */

.about-section p {

    color: #333; /* Dark text color for readability */

    font-size: 1.3rem;

    line-height: 1.6;

}

/* Address Card Styles */

.address-cards {

    display: flex;

    flex-wrap: wrap;

    gap: 20px;

    justify-content: center;

}

.address-card {

    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f4f4f4); /* Subtle gradient */

    border: 1px solid #ddd;

    border-radius: 12px; /* Rounded corners */

    padding: 20px;

    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Shadow effect */

    width: 100%;

    max-width: 300px; /* Responsive width */

    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; /* Smooth transition */

}

.address-card:hover {

    transform: scale(1.02); /* Slight zoom on hover */

    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Enhanced shadow on hover */

}

.address-title {

    color: #17a2b8; /* Teal Blue for card titles */

    margin-top: 0;

    font-size: 1.4rem;

    border-bottom: 2px solid #17a2b8; /* Teal Blue underline */

    padding-bottom: 5px;

}


</style>